you don't know me or something.

461
00:35:57,400 --> 00:35:58,519
I'm not drunk.

462
00:36:02,039 --> 00:36:03,000
No?

463
00:36:04,239 --> 00:36:05,199
No.

464
00:36:22,199 --> 00:36:23,480
What do you want to do?

465
00:36:26,400 --> 00:36:30,119
-We can't go to my house.
-And yours, no chance.

466
00:36:34,159 --> 00:36:35,400
There's a place,

467
00:36:37,119 --> 00:36:37,960
but...

468
00:36:52,679 --> 00:36:58,000
