to bring you here.

470
00:37:07,880 --> 00:37:10,920
-I'm sorry.
-It was what it was meant to be.

471
00:37:11,760 --> 00:37:12,880
Relax. I'm fine.

472
00:37:14,639 --> 00:37:16,239
